# RKAA

RKAA la bo khung ban dau cho du an RAN KPI Anomaly Analyzer.

## Yeu cau

- Python 3.11+

## Chay local

```bash
uvicorn rkaa.main:app --reload
```

## Kiem tra chat luong

```bash
ruff check .
pytest
coverage run -m pytest
coverage report
```

## Health check

`GET /health` tra ve HTTP 200 va trang thai `ok`.
